## 3. The Hybrid Story Generation Model

The core innovation is how Tier 2 (Apple FM) and Tier 3 (Gemini) cooperate on a single story without either blocking the other.

### The Dual-Track Pattern

```
Button press on AiSee
       │
       ▼
Tier 2: Privacy pipeline runs (≈600ms)
       │
       ├──── TRACK A (immediate) ──────────────────────────────┐
       │     Apple FoundationModels                            │
       │     → StoryBeat in ≈400ms                             │
       │     → Speaks to child immediately                     │
       │     → Sends beat summary to Tier 3 via /sync/beat     │
       │                                                       ▼
       └──── TRACK B (async, ≈2-4s) ──────────────────────────┤
             POST /story/beat to Tier 3                        │
             → Context Enricher reads Firestore long memory    │
             → Enhanced Story Generator calls Gemini 2.0 Flash │
             → Safety Moderator validates output               │
             → Enhanced beat stored in Firestore               │
             → iOS app receives enhanced beat for NEXT turn    ◄┘
                    (child currently listening to Track A)
```

**Track A always plays.** Track B enhances the following turn. The child never waits for the cloud. If Track B is slower than expected, Track A plays for the current turn AND the next turn. Tier 3 beats queue and play when available.

